{
  "stem": "24231.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in-- people in Czechoslovakia always thought that something like that cannot happen, the Jews in Czechoslovakia, cannot happen among the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no-- there was-- we, we knew what was going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, I had an uncle who was in, in, in a business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a jewelry business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in 1938 when, when, when the Germans came to Prague, he packed up and went to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was telling his brothers, look, there is-- look what's happening in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it's going to happen here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nobody, at that time, imagined that something like this could-- would have happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so all, all my-- all my uncles and aunts, they stayed with the exception of this one brother who went to Switzerland, and to England, and eventually to the United States.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the uncle who brought me over, over here after the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what-- the first thing what happened is when we started to wear-- started to wear stars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what happened is, as a kid, all of a sudden, you imagine all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember one time when I was going to school in, in Prague, I was in the back and there was a little old lady who had chocolate.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I haven't had chocolate in, I don't know, about two years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she offered me a bar of chocolate, and I, I was so suspicious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't take the chocolate because I thought it was poison.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I, I started to get suspicious of everybody because you got kicked out of the trolley cars.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on top of that, one day the Jews had to get inside the house at eight o'clock.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a curfew after eight o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
